{"tid":277698,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"2020東京奧運宣布新設3-on-3 籃球賽","createTime":"2017-06-09T22:29:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-10T04:01:31.000Z","uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"cd77ae8ea2e4ea66c76ef94f489c9efbb3928122","tid":277698,"uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T22:29:40.000Z","msg":"Olympics adds 3-on-3 basketball as a new event for 2020 in Toyko<br />\nThree-on-three basketball has officially made the final cut for the 2020 Tokyo Olympics. The International Olympics Committee finalized the news on Friday in a widely expected press release.<br />\n<br />\nThe IOC met on Friday to determine who will host the 2024 and 2028 Summer Olympics, at which time three-on-three basketball was also made official.<br />\n<br />\nIOC officials see three-on-three basketball as a chance to add a popular urban team sport to a schedule that already includes two urban individual sports &mdash; skateboarding and sport climbing.<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;The fascinating new events that we approved today, together with the five new sports that were added to the Tokyo 2020 programm last year, represent a step-change in the Olympic programm. I am delighted that the Olympic Games in Tokyo will be more youthful, more urban and will include more women&rdquo;, IOC President Thomas Bach said in the press release.<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.sbnation.com/platform/amp/nba/2017/6/4/15737184/olympics-3-on-3-basketball-tokyo-2020\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.sbnation.com%2Fplatform%2Famp%2Fnba%2F2017%2F6%2F4%2F15737184%2Folympics-3-on-3-basketball-tokyo-2020&d=EJSBKswcsDeyrrrmgNYb6UjIoeaDRyeQRMy%2FzT52C%2Fo%3D&h=3fd12abe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.sbnation.com/platform/amp/nba/2017/6/4/15737184/olympics-3-on-3-basketball-tokyo-2020</a><br />\n美國求其出隊都玩晒"},{"pid":"7a66f8a9f82bc585464736feee965f3d4a920107","tid":277698,"uid":51978,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0